### 修复 Admin 用户分店问题的解决方案

### 1. 重新初始化数据（推荐）
GET http://localhost:5001/api/debug/init-data
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 2. 检查当前用户分店状况
GET http://localhost:5001/api/users/stores
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 3. 获取所有分店（检查是否有分店数据）
GET http://localhost:5001/api/stores
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 4. 手动为当前用户分配默认分店（如果存在）
POST http://localhost:5001/api/stores/assign-user
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "storeGuid": "default",
    "userGuid": "admin"
}

###

### 5. 创建默认分店（如果不存在）
POST http://localhost:5001/api/stores
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "storeCode": "DEFAULT",
    "storeName": "Default Store", 
    "address": "Default Store Address",
    "phone": "000-0000-0000",
    "isActive": true
}

###

### 6. 检查修复结果
GET http://localhost:5001/api/users/stores
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}
Content-Type: application/json